It's time to get hot for Jesus and keep our lamps full on a day-to-day basis.

00:35:37.880 --> 00:35:47.590
A lot of you are going to a church that doesn't preach a solid word-based gospel.

00:35:47.590 --> 00:35:57.685
You're going in there getting an itching-ear gospel for 30 minutes with fog machines and lights.

00:35:57.685 --> 00:36:01.240
They're losing the purity of preaching repentance.

00:36:01.240 --> 00:36:08.497
It's so important that you understand filling your lamps full of oil.

00:36:08.497 --> 00:36:19.120
I've warned you what the Lord told me: half will be taken, half will be left.

00:36:19.120 --> 00:36:22.740
Which one are you?

00:36:22.740 --> 00:36:24.555
Don't put it off.

00:36:24.555 --> 00:36:42.600
There was a man in the comment section who said he could live like a heathen for a while because it doesn't sound like he's coming back soon.

00:36:42.600 --> 00:36:46.520
Why would you gamble your soul?

00:36:46.520 --> 00:36:49.631
No man is promised tomorrow.

00:36:50.102 --> 00:36:53.379
You could die tonight in your sleep.

00:36:53.379 --> 00:37:08.319
People think they can sow their wild oats and serve Jesus ten years from now, but they die nine years into it and are in hell for eternity.

00:37:22.235 --> 00:37:22.400
The wages of sin is death.

00:37:22.400 --> 00:37:30.594
It's time today to ask Jesus to be your Lord and Savior.

00:37:30.594 --> 00:37:37.326
Are you ready to stand at that great white throne of judgment?

00:37:37.326 --> 00:37:42.190
When he says, 'What did you do for me?

00:37:42.190 --> 00:37:44.960
' will your cup be empty?

00:37:45.164 --> 00:37:46.793
I pray God has mercy.

00:37:46.793 --> 00:37:48.693
We're running out of time.

00:37:48.693 --> 00:37:55.380
I always look for him during the September timeframe, during Rosh Hashanah.

00:37:55.380 --> 00:37:57.566
Could it be this year?

00:37:57.566 --> 00:38:05.177
I've rambled on long enough, but I wanted you to see the parallels.

00:38:05.177 --> 00:38:11.159
God is speaking to different prophetic voices to warn them.

00:38:11.159 --> 00:38:14.613
He put us to be a watchman on the wall.

00:38:15.635 --> 00:38:22.079
I feel like I'm Paul Revere riding my horse through the towns telling the minutemen, 'Jesus is coming!

00:38:26.667 --> 00:38:26.973
Jesus is coming!

00:38:26.973 --> 00:38:33.205
' to get you woke up for the spiritual war.

00:38:33.205 --> 00:38:42.040
Father, I thank you for every single person.

00:38:42.040 --> 00:38:42.880
Say, 'Jesus, come into my heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
I make you my Lord and personal Savior.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
' He made it so a little child can get saved; it's easy.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Father, I thank you for healings and wholeness in these people's homes.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
We call in unsaved loved ones in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Angels, go out and bring them home.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
We're running out of time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
Our children, wayward husbands, moms, and dads—we call them home in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
We thank you that you don't want one to perish.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
We bind the demonic distractions and spirits that would hold them down and command you to release our loved ones.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
We call the harvest of souls in the name of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Father, give us creative ideas to bring souls into your kingdom.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
I thank you for the anointing of the Holy Ghost to flow through us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
It's time for a great new outpouring of your spirit—new wine and new wineskins.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Fan the flame in these people today in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
We call for a fullness of fire, like gasoline on a flame.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
I want to tell you all thank you for watching.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
If you could click the notification bell, it really would bless us.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.300
If you could like the video and put a comment down below, we're curious where your heart's at.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
We thank you all for your support.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
You're helping get the gospel spread throughout the world.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.950
Another person gave their heart to Jesus and some got baptized in the Holy Ghost this week.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Thank you for all your love and kindness.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.150
God bless you all; Jesus loves you so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.100
We will see you next time.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Y'all have a blessed and wonderful day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
